\begin{document}
$\frac{1}{{{{\tau }_{{\mathrm{scattering}}}}}}$\end{document}), which can be a prerequisite for polaron formation. Next, we will focus on the discussion of short-range EPI and polaron formation in 4AMP samples and provide evidence that the spin lifetime enhancement originates from the small polaron effect.

